      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="04115-102"><xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.NetworkChange>类提供了地址更改通知，通过引发<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.NetworkChange.NetworkAddressChanged>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="04115-102">The <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.NetworkChange> class provides address change notification by raising <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.NetworkChange.NetworkAddressChanged> events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="04115-103">多种原因，例如断开连接的网络电缆，移出的无线局域网或硬件故障的范围可以更改接口地址。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="04115-103">An interface address can change for many reasons, such as a disconnected network cable, moving out of range of a wireless Local Area Network, or hardware failure.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="04115-104">若要接收通知，必须确定应用程序的事件处理程序，它是一个或多个执行每次引发事件的特定于应用程序的任务的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="04115-104">To receive notification, you must identify your application's event handlers, which are one or more methods that perform your application-specific tasks each time the event is raised.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="04115-105">能够<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.NetworkChange>对象调用事件处理方法时<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.NetworkChange.NetworkAddressChanged>事件发生时，必须将关联的方法与<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.NetworkAddressChangedEventHandler>委托，并将此委托添加到该事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="04115-105">To have a <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.NetworkChange> object call your event-handling methods when a <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.NetworkChange.NetworkAddressChanged> event occurs, you must associate the methods with a <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.NetworkAddressChangedEventHandler> delegate, and add this delegate to the event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
